messages.messageBody:
--Hi Folks

sorry i did not make it to the armouries. The weather
turned really bad here. Several trees were blown down
in my area and I didnt think it was safe to drive up
there.

I do go regular to the armouries as I have family in
the area, and I train at a dojo near by.

If anyone is after any photos of any part of the
displays I will be more than happy to take digital
photos and email them out

Paul Richardson
